Detailed Description

The section has a list of all internal data structures which are used internally by the mmWave module.

Typedef Documentation

typedef struct MMWave_BpmChirp_t MMWave_BpmChirp

mmWave BPM configuration

The structure is used to keep track of the BPM configurations

typedef struct MMWave_Chirp_t MMWave_Chirp

mmWave Chirp configuration

The structure is used to keep track of the chirps which have been configured in the system.

typedef struct MMWave_MCB_t MMWave_MCB

mmWave Control MCB

The structure is used to store all the relevant information required to execute the mmWave control module.

typedef struct MMWave_Profile_t MMWave_Profile

mmWave Profile configuration

The structure is used to keep track of the profiles

typedef struct MMWave_SpawnFxnNode_t MMWave_SpawnFxnNode

mmWave Spawn function entry

The structure is used to keep track of the spawn functions which need to be executed by the control module.
